Let's think again. The multiset `S` is `Multiset.join (Multiset.replicate P.M (Multiset.Ico (P.n - P.n / P.M) P.n))`. The sum of `m.factorization p` over `S` should be `P.M * (Finset.filter (p ∣ ·) (Finset.Ico (P.n - P.n / P.M) P.n)).card`.

